{
  "id": "69ccda0895fee474f428116a",
  "title": "近親婚問題",
  "created": 1775032843,
  "updated": 1775055532,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ccda0895fee474f428116a",
      "text": "近親婚問題",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775032843,
      "updated": 1775032843
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccda0b00000000003322b0",
      "text": "まずどういう問題があるんだ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775032843,
      "updated": 1775032851
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccda1000000000003322b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775032849,
      "updated": 1775032849
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccde11000000000071a7a5",
      "text": "3親等内の血族の結婚は禁じられている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775033874,
      "updated": 1775033875
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccde56000000000071a7a7",
      "text": "code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775033943,
      "updated": 1775033948
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccde5d000000000071a7a8",
      "text": " graph",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775033949,
      "updated": 1775033954
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce05a000000000071a7b2",
      "text": " hmmm(曾祖父3) & hmmf(曽祖母3)-->hmmc(❤️)-->imm;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775034459,
      "updated": 1775034459
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce05b000000000071a7b3",
      "text": " hmfm(曾祖父3) & hmff(曽祖母3)-->hfmc(❤️)-->imf;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775034459,
      "updated": 1775034482
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf282000000000071a82a",
      "text": " hfmm(曾祖父3) & hfmf(曽祖母3)-->hmfc(❤️)-->ifm;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775039106,
      "updated": 1775039136
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce05c000000000071a7b5",
      "text": " hffm(曾祖父3) & hfff(曽祖母3)-->hffc(❤️)-->iff & iff5(4<br>大伯父<br>大伯母<br>大伯父<br>大叔母);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775034460,
      "updated": 1775038709
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce01a000000000071a7b1",
      "text": " imm(祖父2) & imf(祖母2)-->imc(❤️)-->jm3(父1) & jm1(3<br>伯父<br>伯母<br>叔父<br>叔母) ;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775034395,
      "updated": 1775038614
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce669000000000071a7d8",
      "text": " jm1-->jmc(❤️)-->k11(4<br>従兄<br>従姉<br>従弟<br>従妹)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036009,
      "updated": 1775050346
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce160000000000071a7b7",
      "text": " ifm(祖父2) & iff(祖母2)-->ifc(❤️);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775034721,
      "updated": 1775038767
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce426000000000071a7ce",
      "text": " ifc(❤️)-->jf3(母1);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775035656,
      "updated": 1775038623
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce421000000000071a7cd",
      "text": " jm3(父1) & jf3(母1)-->jc(❤️)-->k3 & k5(2<br>兄<br>姉<br>弟<br>妹);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775035426,
      "updated": 1775039130
    },
    {
      "id": "69cceb33000000000071a7ef",
      "text": " iff5-->iff5c(❤️);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775039130,
      "updated": 1775039130
    },
    {
      "id": "69cceb25000000000071a7ed",
      "text": " iff5c(❤️)-->jff51(5<br>伯従父<br>伯従母<br>叔従父<br>叔従母);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775039130,
      "updated": 1775050300
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf218000000000071a829",
      "text": " k3(本人)-->kc(❤️)-->l(子1);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775039000,
      "updated": 1775050298
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1eeb0000000000761080",
      "text": " k5-->k5c(❤️)-->l51(甥3) & l52(姪3);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050476,
      "updated": 1775050476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf175000000000071a809",
      "text": " l-->lc(❤️)-->m(孫2);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775038837,
      "updated": 1775050442
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf15e000000000071a805",
      "text": " m-->mc(❤️)-->n(曾孫3);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775038814,
      "updated": 1775050316
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf1c3000000000071a81a",
      "text": " jff51-->jff51c(❤️)-->kff511(6<br>再従兄<br>再従姉<br>再従弟<br>再従妹);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775038915,
      "updated": 1775038915
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccf1c3000000000071a81b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775038915,
      "updated": 1775050329
    },
    {
      "id": "69ccde12000000000071a7a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775033874,
      "updated": 1775033874
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce6db0000000000b56b3d",
      "text": " よく聞くのは[血が濃くなる]から[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1775036128,
      "updated": 1775036146
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce6f30000000000b56b3f",
      "text": "  [ハプスブルク家]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1775036147,
      "updated": 1775036272
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce71b000000000071a7dc",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ハプスブルク家の顎][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036187,
      "updated": 1775036206
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce75f000000000071a7de",
      "text": "\t\t\tおーい。私がリンクつけたからもういいぞー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036256,
      "updated": 1775036271
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce77500000000000778b3",
      "text": "\t\t\tスマホだと編集しづらくて終わりを感じました[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1775036277,
      "updated": 1775036293
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce6de0000000000b56b3e",
      "text": "\t\tこの表現には多義性による問題があるんよね[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036129,
      "updated": 1775036187
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce718000000000071a7db",
      "text": "\t\t\t「血」を生物学的な遺伝性の意味で考えることもあるし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036185,
      "updated": 1775036227
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce742000000000071a7dd",
      "text": "\t\t\t「社会的な血族関係」の意味で考えることもある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036227,
      "updated": 1775036298
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce78c000000000071a7df",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t相続の問題",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036300,
      "updated": 1775036303
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce7e0000000000070504f",
      "text": "\tそういえば、近親婚は禁止されているけど、近親相姦は禁止されていないのでは",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1775036385,
      "updated": 1775036410
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce8020000000000705050",
      "text": "\t 禁止されているというか、刑法における記述の有無",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1775036419,
      "updated": 1775036433
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce89f000000000071a7e2",
      "text": "\t 調べたらホントだった[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036576,
      "updated": 1775036588
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce8ab000000000071a7e3",
      "text": "\t \t多分他の条文を組み合わせて捌くんだろうけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036588,
      "updated": 1775036603
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce8d2000000000071a7e4",
      "text": " \t尊属殺人は禁止したくせに、そっちは禁止しないのか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036627,
      "updated": 1775036948
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce9b3000000000071a7e6",
      "text": "  \t昔尊属殺人罪があった頃に、父親に虐待＋近親姦（相ではなかろう）をされた娘が父親を殺して有罪判決を受けた事件があったのを思い出して呟いた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036852,
      "updated": 1775036940
    },
    {
      "id": "69cce94a000000000071a7e5",
      "text": "\tそもそも先天性疾患に関するリスク的にはそれほど問題ないみたいな話があっておもろい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775036746,
      "updated": 1775055522
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd327b0000000000817db0",
      "text": "\t\t[近親婚と先天性疾患の関係]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775055483,
      "updated": 1775055532
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd32760000000000817daf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775055479,
      "updated": 1775055479
    }
  ]
}